_:N91e48f1060ae4ef1b5e7107d2bdddead <http://schema.org/description> "<p>Seth Kybird is interim Chief Executive Officer at Nuclear Waste Services (NWS). Before joining NWS in April 2025, Seth was CEO at <a rel=\"external\" href=\"https://nucleartransportsolutions.com/\">Nuclear Transport Solutions (NTS)</a> since its formation in 2021, and previously Managing Director of International Nuclear Services (INS).</p>\n\n<p>He is also a former strategy consultant and chartered accountant. Having previously worked at NDA, KPMG, and Deloitte, Seth has experience of leading and developing organisations, and a strong track record in tackling complex commercial challenges in the UK and internationally.</p>\n" .
